OL,3,C'Unsustainable' Royal Mail could cut
OL,4,Cdeliveries down to three days a week
OL,6,FThe regulator said that two main
OL,7,Foptions are being mooted, cutting the
OL,8,Fsix-day a week service to five days or
OL,9,Fthree.
OL,11,FHowever, either of those would require
OL,12,Fgovernment and parliament to change
OL,13,Fcurrent laws, with another proposal
OL,14,Fbeing to overhaul first and second
OL,15,Fclass and business services.
OL,17,FSuch a move could see the introduction
OL,18,Fof a service where most deliveries
OL,19,Ftake up to three days or longer, with
OL,20,Fa next-day service still available for
OL,21,Fany urgent letters.
