OL,3,C'Unsustainable' Royal Mail could cut
OL,4,Cdeliveries down to three days a week
OL,6,FOfcom said Royal Mail could make cost
OL,7,Fsavings of #100 million to #200
OL,8,Fmillion if letter deliveries were
OL,9,Freduced to five days; and #400 million
OL,10,Fto #650 million if reduced to three
OL,11,Fdays.
OL,13,FIts savings could be up to #650
OL,14,Fmillion if the large majority of
OL,15,Fletters were delivered within three
OL,16,Fdays.
