OL,3,C'Unsustainable' Royal Mail could cut
OL,4,Cdeliveries down to three days a week
OL,6,FOfcom chief executive Dame Melanie
OL,7,FDawes said: "Postal workers are part
OL,8,Fof the fabric of our society and are
OL,9,Fcritical to communities up and down
OL,10,Fthe country.
OL,12,F"But we're sending half as many
OL,13,Fletters as we did in 2011, and
OL,14,Freceiving many more parcels. The
OL,15,Funiversal service hasn't changed since
OL,16,Fthen, it's getting out of date and
OL,17,Fwill become unsustainable if we don't
OL,18,Ftake action.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/6
