OL,3,C'Unsustainable' Royal Mail could cut
OL,4,Cdeliveries down to three days a week
OL,6,F"So we've set out options for reform
OL,7,Fso there can be a national discussion
OL,8,Fabout the future of universal post.
OL,10,F"In the meantime, we're making sure
OL,11,Fprices will remain affordable by
OL,12,Fcapping the price of second class
OL,13,Fstamps."
OL,15,FCommenting on the Ofcom review,
OL,16,FLiberal Democrat Treasury Spokesperson
OL,17,FSarah Olney MP said: "This feels like
OL,18,Fa slap in the face for so many who
OL,19,Falready have the pain of delayed
OL,20,Fdeliveries. We shouldn't be receiving
OL,21,Fa second class service.
