OL,3,C'Unsustainable' Royal Mail could cut
OL,4,Cdeliveries down to three days a week
OL,6,F"Regular deliveries are what the
OL,7,Fcountry has come to expect. For a
OL,8,Fcompany already struggling to meet its
OL,9,Fdelivery targets, this doesn't sit
OL,10,Fright."
OL,12,FHowever, despite the suggestions from
OL,13,FOfcom, Postal Affairs Minister Kevin
OL,14,FHollinrake said that government was
OL,15,Fcommitted to a six-day service from
OL,16,Fthe Royal Mail.
OL,18,FHe said: "I believe the Royal Mail can
OL,19,Fbuild a sustainable model. But that
OL,20,Fsustainable model must be based on a-
OL,21,Fsix day service."
